text:
[Verse]
Wake up to the sky
New day let's fly
Colors in our eyes
Let's dance until the night

[Verse]
Feel the rhythm flow
Hearts begin to glow
Time is moving slow
Let’s let the music grow

[Chorus]
One more sunrise
Chasing the skies
One more sunrise
Light in our eyes

[Verse]
Steps and shadows play
Through the light of day
Mind begins to sway
Love guides us all the way

[Verse]
Silhouettes in gold
Inside stories told
Memories we hold
Together we are bold

[Chorus]
One more sunrise
Chasing the skies
One more sunrise
Light in our eyes
title: One More Sunrise
